window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Upon its first publication, this path breaking book launched an explosion of interest in how Eastern spirituality can enhance Western psychology. Since then, the worlds of Buddhism and psychotherapy have been forged into a revolutionary new understanding of what constitutes a healthy emotional life. </p> <p>In his insightful introduction, Mark Epstein reflects on this revolution and considers how it is likely to evolve in the future. </p>"; 
